                        srcset="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/07/books/review/07WARNER/07WARNER-videoLarge.jpg 768w, https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/07/books/review/07WARNER/07WARNER-mediumThreeByTwo440.jpg 440w, https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/07/books/review/07WARNER/07WARNER-mediumThreeByTwo225.jpg 225w, https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/07/books/review/07WARNER/07WARNER-hpSmall.jpg 163w, https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/07/books/review/07WARNER/07WARNER-thumbLarge.jpg 150w"
                        alt=""
                    />
                                                        </a>
                <figcaption class="caption" itemprop="caption description">
                    <span class="credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder"><span class="visually-hidden">Credit</span>Emily Baxter</span>
                </figcaption>
            </figure>
                <div class="story-body">
            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/05/books/review/what-it-means-when-a-man-falls-from-the-sky-lesley-nneka-arimah-.html" data-tracking-index="9" data-rref="">August’s Book Club Pick: ‘What It Means When a Man Falls From the Sky,’ by Lesley Nneka Arimah</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">A debut story collection that looks to Nigeria’s past, present and possibly fantastical future.</p>
            <p class="byline">
                <span class="freshness"><time data-utc-timestamp="1493974833" datetime="1493974833"></time></span>
                                <span class="divider"></span>
                                <span class="author" itemprop="author">By MARINA WARNER</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>
</li>
                </ol>
        </div>
                    <div class="rank-template template-3">
            <ol class="story-menu">
            
            <li>
    <article class="story theme-summary ">
                    <h3 class="kicker">Now Read This</h3>
