            </figure>
                <div class="story-body">
            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/02/02/books/review/pachinko-min-jin-lee.html" data-tracking-index="10" data-rref="">July’s Book Club Pick: ‘Pachinko,’ by Min Jin Lee</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">Home but Not Home: Four Generations of an Ethnic Korean Family in Japan</p>
